Cloneable, Map<String,Object>
public final class ActivityContentDetails
extends GenericJson

JSON template for the contentDetails part of a activity.

This is the Java data model class that specifies how to parse/serialize into the JSON that is transmitted over HTTP when working with the YouTube API. For a detailed explanation see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json

Author:
Google, Inc.
